          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By authors:",
                " 1.A new beamline was installed including two",
                "quadrupole tripletts,which provided an improved",
                "matching of the beam optics with the aperture of the",
                "gas target system about 100% transmission.In order to",
                "maintain this transmission at low energies,it was",
                "necessary to shorten one half of the dynamitron",
                "cascade.",
                " 2.In order to minimize the yield contributions from",
                "background reactions in particular from C-13(A,N)O-16,",
                "all beam-line components of the gas target system have",
                "been sand-blaster (glass) and the target chamber was",
                "lined with Ta.",
                " 3.The cylindrical extended target chamber was",
                "surrounded by 8 He-3 proportional counters,each of",
                " 2.5-cm diameter and about 1-m length, which were",
                "embedded in a cylindrical polyethylene moderator of",
                " 35-cm diameter. This 4-pi neutron detector was",
                "surrounded in addition with layers of polyethylene,",
                "paraffine, boron and cadmium to reduce the beam-",
                "independent background rate.",
                " 4.At each beam energy,differential measurements of the",
                "neutron yields with gas-in and gas-out have been made.",
                " 5.The beam energy has been determined directly by",
                "gamma spectroscopy in the whole energy range using the",
                "direct capture reaction He-3(A,G)Be-7."
              ]
            }
          ],
